# FILE: studentDashboard/learningVault/enrolledCourses.desc
# ROLE: Academy Learning Terminal
# ROUTE: /dashboard/learning
# ACCOUNT: Student only
# THEME: Dark · progress-driven · cinematic hero card

## 1. CONTINUE WATCHING HERO (Top Fold)
- CARD STYLE: bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6366F1]/12 to-[#8B5CF6]/6 · border-[#6366F1]/25 · rounded-2xl
- THUMBNAIL: blurred lesson preview (16:9) with play button overlay
- DATA: Course Title + current Lesson name
- PROGRESS BAR: thin indigo bar below title (percentage text right-aligned)
- TIME LEFT: "3س 12د لإتمام الدورة"
- ACTION: [▶️ متابعة التعلم] — gradient-bg button

## 2. ENROLLED COURSE INVENTORY
- FILTER TABS: [🟢 جارية] [✅ مكتملة]
- LIST STYLE: vertical stack of rows
  - THUMBNAIL: 16:9 · rounded-xl · play overlay on hover
  - TITLE: text-[#F1F5F9] font-medium
  - PROGRESS BAR: glow-bar (width = % complete)
  - CERT STATUS: [🔒 محجوب] until 100% · [📜 متاحة] when complete
  - ACTION: [▶️ متابعة] → /academy/course/:id

## 3. CURRICULUM DRAWER (Expandable per Course)
- Clicking a course expands full lesson list
- LESSON STATUS: ✅ مكتملة · ⚪ الحالي · 🔒 مقفل
- Includes video duration + link to lesson in course page

## 4. SKILL ACQUISITION BADGES
- Row of earned skill orbs: [⚛️ React] [🌿 MongoDB] [🎨 UI Design]
- TOTAL XP FROM LEARNING: "+1,400 XP" — gradient-text
- MILESTONE: "دورتان أخريان للوصول إلى مرتبة 'محترف'"

## 5. ACTIONS BAR
- [🎓 تصفح دورات جديدة] → /academy
- [📜 شهاداتي] → shows all completed course certificates
